name: Cosmic Dragon, Cinder
effect:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
During your opponent's turn, when your opponent activates a Spell/Trap Card or monster effect (Quick Effect): You can discard 1 Trap; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy it. During your Main Phase 2, if this card did not attack this turn: You can make your opponent discard 1 card. You can only use each effect of "Cosmic Dragon, Cinder" once per turn.
